00:04:01.390 --> 00:04:04.420
And I wanted to send
some of the works

00:04:04.420 --> 00:04:06.070
that I'm most excited about--

00:04:06.070 --> 00:04:06.510
SPEAKER: Oh, very nice.

00:04:06.510 --> 00:04:07.750
YOLANDA GONZALEZ: --which
are some still lifes

00:04:07.750 --> 00:04:08.596
and some portraits.

00:04:08.596 --> 00:04:09.970
And these are
portraits of people

00:04:09.970 --> 00:04:15.880
that I know that are dear to me,
that represent strength, power,

00:04:15.880 --> 00:04:17.819
positive energy, and love.

00:04:17.819 --> 00:04:18.610
SPEAKER: Thank you.

00:04:18.610 --> 00:04:19.779
And now that we're
in the subject,

00:04:19.779 --> 00:04:21.237
I noticed that two
of the paintings

00:04:21.237 --> 00:04:22.725
are called Diana something.

00:04:22.725 --> 00:04:24.490
Who is this Diana person?

00:04:24.490 --> 00:04:26.170
YOLANDA GONZALEZ:
