00:04:42.970 --> 00:04:45.040
And she's just a
brilliant woman.

00:04:45.040 --> 00:04:46.785
Brilliant, powerful woman.

00:04:46.785 --> 00:04:47.410
SPEAKER: Great.

00:04:47.410 --> 00:04:48.100
That's so nice.

00:04:48.100 --> 00:04:50.750
Do they have this artwork
