00:12:54.350 --> 00:12:57.130
I mean, a Latina, a
woman, basically, you're

00:12:57.130 --> 00:12:58.370
an entrepreneur.

00:12:58.370 --> 00:13:02.690
How hard is it in the art world
to be a Latina and a woman

00:13:02.690 --> 00:13:05.730
in a business that's--

