But having arrived
here three years ago,

00:17:26.619 --> 00:17:31.270
I found an art community here
that was just very inviting,

00:17:31.270 --> 00:17:32.140
very giving.

00:17:32.140 --> 00:17:36.790
Like finding these strongholds,
like these beautiful, powerful

00:17:36.790 --> 00:17:39.880
women, like Chicana art is--

00:17:39.880 --> 00:17:41.620
that'll give you--

