00:18:02.530 --> 00:18:05.410
to help each other out, which is
something that you don't really

00:18:05.410 --> 00:18:07.920
find in a lot of places.

00:18:07.920 --> 00:18:11.860
It's a lot of power here within
the art community and Chicanas,

00:18:11.860 --> 00:18:13.060
Latinas in general.

00:18:13.060 --> 00:18:14.643
SPEAKER: So are you
paying it forward?

