Do you mentor?

00:18:18.757 --> 00:18:20.090
Tell us a little bit about that.

00:18:20.090 --> 00:18:21.865
Like what do you do to--

00:18:21.865 --> 00:18:25.830
so to give to the
next generation?

00:18:25.830 --> 00:18:26.890
[INAUDIBLE] you teach?

00:18:26.890 --> 00:18:29.800
ROSALIE LOPEZ: Right
